                <supplied reason="lost">Ἑλβιδία</supplied>ν <supplied reason="lost">Λ</supplied>αοδίκην, θυγατέρα Ἑλβιδ<supplied reason="lost">ίου <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>μένου Διογένους γυναῖκα <supplied reason="lost">ψηφίσ</supplied><lb break="no" n="3"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ματι</supplied> τῆ<supplied reason="lost">ς β</supplied>ουλῆς καὶ τοῦ δήμο<supplied reason="lost">υ σωφρο</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">σύνης ἕ</supplied>ν<supplied reason="lost">ε</supplied>κεν καὶ φιλανδρίας <supplied reason="lost">καὶ τῆς</supplied> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">πάσης κοσ</supplied>μιότητός τε καὶ ἀρ<supplied reason="lost">ετῆς <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="6"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> Θεόδωρος καὶ Φ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
            </ab></div>
